activity.text:
I investigated the issue, so when the token expires, the user is logged out and redirected to the page /session-expired.
So in this case all works correctly.
The issue occurs for logged-in users if manually enter /session-expired in the URL.
Users see a 404 page because in the router configuration for logged-in users, there is no such route (session-expired)
So possible solution is to not allow logged-in users to enter this route, it should be allowed only for non-logged users.
I need your approval @rithviknishad
